{"tid":2470244,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支那女脫衣不慎拉鍊夾住眼皮　醫生也沒轍靠消防員解圍","createTime":"2021-03-31T20:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T00:59:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2016f5e9b391e68f6d7a50aae55e4153874fda16","tid":2470244,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T20:03:50.000Z","msg":"被拉鍊夾到皮膚的經驗可能不太常見，但只要被夾過就知道，真會讓人痛不欲生。中國浙江省一名女子，日前在脫掉帶有拉鍊的外套時，一個不小心拉鍊夾住了她的右眼眼皮！<br />\n<br />\n《新華網》報導，中國浙江杭州一名女子，周日(28日)要脫掉外套時，沒注意到拉鍊的位置，用力一拉竟然夾住了她右眼的上眼皮，雖然試著想要扯開，卻實在太痛只得趕快就醫。沒想到到了醫院急診室，醫生也束手無策，最後只能打電話找消防隊求助。<br />\n<br />\n消防員到場後，先用剪刀把多餘的衣服剪掉，接著拿鉗子一點一點地破壞拉鍊，終於在20分鐘後順利將女子眼皮從拉鍊中移出。<br />\n<br />\n女子眼皮雖然已經發紅腫脹，但在醫師治療後已無大礙。（於慶中／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210331/XB44YZDUZRHH7KJGNSTAAV45IQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210331%2FXB44YZDUZRHH7KJGNSTAAV45IQ%2F&d=6VUJY1vbA2ifZxBcTMZdIy9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=2f041033\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210331%2FXB44YZDUZRHH7KJGNSTAAV45IQ%2F&h=31b983e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210331/XB44YZDUZRHH7KJGNSTAAV45IQ/</a>"},{"pid":"2b1e6f6b6645b182aa9d3f34278c63854844f085","tid":2470244,"uid":3852,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T20:20:16.000Z","msg":"拉鏈外套嚟？點除先會夾到眼皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044f8eb80e9c1266eb60a2a55c041355fa150597","tid":2470244,"uid":208713,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T20:21:30.000Z","msg":"你包埋個頭出街？"},{"pid":"0d796426727a2b289074621c327ffc38a86d8d16","tid":2470244,"uid":208713,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T20:21:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢包埋個頭出街？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b2bd3439e1703c35d2edd84051ad1b52e6966827","tid":2470244,"uid":17359,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score